Interface AtomSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GIterable<Atom>, Iterable<Atom>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GraphAtomSet, InMemoryAtomSet, RdbmsStore, Store, TripleStore
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAtomSet, AbstractInMemoryAtomSet, AbstractRdbmsStore, AbstractTripleStore, BlueprintsGraphDBStore, DefaultInMemoryGraphAtomSet, DefaultRdbmsStore, GraphDBStore, JenaStore, LinkedListAtomSet, Neo4jStore, PlainTableRDBMSStore, SailStore

    public interface AtomSet
extends GIterable<Atom>
    This interface represents a set of atoms.
